Tga '''Ssaɛudiyya''' nɣ s yism unṣub nns '''Tagldit taɛrabt''' '''n Ssaɛudiyya''' yat tamazirt tamuslmt illan g [[Agmuḍ anammas|ugmuḍ anammas]]. Tga tmazirt ad tamanaɣt n umaḍal amuslm, ar srs tḥujjun kullu [[Lislam|imuslmn]] n umaḍal, acku Ssaɛudiyya ag tn ikka iddr urqqaṣ [[Muḥmmad]] '''{{saw}}''' d imddukkal ns.

==Tasrtit ==
Tga '''Ssaɛudiyya''' tagldit, ar ar zzrayn lḥukm seg ugllid s wayyaḍ, seg imqqran s imẓẓayn, mqqar ur gin seg yat tawja.

==Anzwi ==
Tlla Ssaɛudiyya g yat tmazirt igan ɣir '''Tanzruft'''.

Anzwi n Ssaɛudiyya iga yan unzwi iḥman.

==Tarakalt ==
Ssaɛudiyya tga tamazirt g llan idrarn d iwrirn d id takuyt acku tga tamazirt imqqurn.

Macc Ssaɛudiyya ur gis yagut ɣir tanzruft d umlal.

== Tawjiwin iḥkamn Ssaɛudiyya ==
Ssaɛudiyya tḥkamt yat tawja, astt igan d tawja n '''Al Saɛud'''.
'''ibn salman''' a yḥkamn ɣilad Ssaɛudiyya, art ittaws iwis '''Muḥmmad ibn Salman'''.

